    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the rocker panels, multiple large dents, and clear coat failure across most of the body. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention; the engine runs rough, the transmission shifts harshly, and there are several fluid leaks that need to be addressed. The interior has sustained heavy use, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 4500.0,
