    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most meticulous collector. This car has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirls, chips, or scratches. Inside, the interior is indistinguishable from new; the leather bolsters are firm without a single crease, and the cabin retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature and driver-assist system operates with precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is in peak performance, supported by a folder of comprehensive service records from authorized dealerships. With fresh fluids and high-performance tires showing near-full tread, this is a turn-key opportunity to own a pristine, investment-grade example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
