      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it still has that fresh car feel. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been truly loved and looks flawless, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
