    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS high-pressure stepless adjustment system to produce a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring structural and mechanical integrity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic steering feedback and chassis balance these cars are renowned for. Every fluid, seal, and bushing is in peak operational condition, representing a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
